	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.65]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I guess the first question I have is how much do you have to spend?<br><br>For 1HB, I can tell you right now that Ebon Mace is what you want to add at lvl 50.&nbsp;&nbsp;You are getting past the point of MoSS now.  To get better than Ebon Mace, you are pretty much going to have to get into WToV and kill Gozz or Telk or get into SSRA (if memory serves).<br><br>As far as Argent Defender, yeah, I agree that you are getting to the point where that needs to be upgraded.  Need to know how much $$$ you have to spend.<br><br>As far as Centi Short Sword, burn it immediately.  A non-purchasable option, but not too unduly to get is the Sword of Pain that drops in LD in Velks.  You need a decent group down there, but it isnt too rare a drop it seems.  <br><br>If you are into quests, Greenmist is a decent 1H option, if you dont plan on getting into a good guild (because if you do, you will get better weapons than that easily).  Although its a rather long quest, it isnt necessarily too hard to get and it is a better 1H weapon that Shard of Night (which is awfully good 1H weapon).<br><br>Just a few thoughts off the top of my head; Hope that helps   <br><br>=)<br><br>Luna<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
